==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Twayblade
<hw>Tway"blade`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several orchidaceous plants which have only two leaves,
as the species of <gen>Listera</gen> and of <gen>Liparis</gen>.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>twyblade</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tweag</ent>⟦br⟧
